org.pragmaticminds.crunch.api.annotations

Annotation Type ParameterValue

  • Deprecated. 
    Part of the old API

    @Deprecated
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=FIELD)
public @interface ParameterValue
    This Annotation is used like ChannelValue but indicates the Value of an Scalar FunctionParameter. This FunctionParameter is injected one (before the Setup Method is called).

    Created by julian on 13.02.17.
